Similar to using the three or four tildes when signing on Talk pages, and using 'subst', in a preview, the result shows up in the preview itself, but the conversion in the edit box is not shown yet. Click on the <tvar name=1><code>{{int|showdiff}}</code></tvar> option to see the change in the wikitext.

